      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "TOP EIGHT (1) wasn't far away at the finish when 4th and beaten only 4.5 lengths (17.01) at Q Straight. Has a good record here at this journey. Remains without a win from the draw but has been in the placings four times from five attempts. Has claims if he runs up to expectations. MULLIGRUB (7) turned spotting a big start finishing eighth (22.77) last time in a P5 at this track. The form out of his last race has been franked. Has ability and is one of the better chances. FINLEY BALE (2) was safely held last time out, finishing eighth at Q Straight over 300m behind Tuta Endless (17.51) in a Grade 5. Expected to feature in the finish.",
